PrecisAppointment of Gilles Rivard as Chairperson and John Gratwick, Clay Gilson, Frank Collins and Horst Sander as members to carry out and report in both official languages to the Minister of Transport on or before January 31, 1993, on a comprehensive review of the operation of any Acts of Parliament for which the Minister of Transport is responsible that pertains to the economic regulation of a mode of transportation.
